<div class="content">
<div class="main-visual">
  <img alt="SPOP 2012" src="/img/ways/index.jpg"/>
</div>

<div class="text">
  <p>All gifts, great and small, make a difference here at UCI. Your gift today can impact research, financial aid, our faculty and our students.</p>
<p>Investing in UCI has never been easier. You may use a credit card, check, money order, electronic funds transfer, or even give appreciated stock or other assets. See the giving details below or contact us directly at 949-824-0142.</p>
<ul type="disc">
<li><a href="http://connect.uci.edu/donate">Online</a></li>
<li><a href="#check">Check / Money Order</a></li>
<li><a href="http://connect.uci.edu/pledge">Pledge Payment</a></li>
<li><a href="#payroll">Payroll Deduction</a></li>
<li><a href="#matching">Matching Companies</a></li>
<li><a href="#eft">Electronic Fund Transfer (EFT)</a></li>
<li><a href="#stock">Stock and Securities</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.plannedgiving.uci.edu/">Planned Giving</a></li>
<li><a href="#Endowed">Endowed Funds</a></li>
<li><a href="#cfg">Corporate and Foundation Giving</a></li>
</ul>
<div align="center"><hr align="center" size="1" width="100%"/></div>
<h3>Online</h3>
<p>Make a gift online</p>
<p><strong>Visit:</strong> <a href="http://connect.uci.edu/donate">http://connect.uci.edu/donate</a></p>
<div align="center"><hr align="center" size="1" width="100%"/></div>
<h3>Pledge Payment</h3>
<p>Make a payment on your pledge</p>
<p><strong>Visit:</strong> <a href="http://connect.uci.edu/pledge">http://connect.uci.edu/pledge</a></p>
<div align="center"><hr align="center" size="1" width="100%"/></div>
<h3><a name="check"></a>Check / Money Order</h3>
<p>Print <a href="http://give.uci.edu/pdf/ways/giftForm.pdf">gift form</a> and mail documents to UC Irvine along with your check or money order.</p>
<p><em>Please do not send cash via U.S. Mail.</em></p>
<p><strong>Print:</strong><a href="http://give.uci.edu/pdf/ways/giftForm.pdf">&#160;Gift form</a></p>
<p><strong> Mail to:</strong></p>
<p><strong>UC Irvine Gift Administration<br/> University Advancement&#160;<br/> 100 Theory, Suite 250&#160;<br/> Irvine, CA 92617</strong></p>
<div align="center"><hr align="center" size="1" width="100%"/></div>
<h3><a name="payroll"></a>UC Irvine Payroll Deduction</h3>
<p><em>If you are a UCI employee, you may authorize UCI's Payroll Department to take a monthly deduction from your paycheck and designate a campus program, school or department to receive your gift.</em></p>
<p>1. Access the&#160;<a href="http://give.uci.edu/pdf/ways/payroll-deduction-form-01.pdf">Payroll Deduction form</a>&#160;online.</p>
<p>2. Print, sign and send this form to the University Advancement Gift Administration Office:</p>
<p><strong>UCI Gift Administration<br/> University Advancement<br/> 100 Theory, Suite 250<br/> Irvine, CA 92617</strong></p>
<p>For more information on a UCI payroll deduction, please contact Gift Administration at 949-824-7631.</p>
<p><strong>NOTE:</strong>&#160;Some employers allow their employees to give to UCI through their own company's payroll reduction plan. To see if your employer offers this service, please contact your employer's human resources or payroll department.&#160;<br/> You may also consult&#160;IRS publication 526.</p>
<div align="center"><hr align="center" size="1" width="100%"/></div>
<h3><a name="matching"></a>Matching Companies</h3>
<p>Some companies match their employees' gifts to universities.<br/> This could double or even triple your gift&#8217;s impact at UCI.</p>
<p><strong>Do you or your spouse/partner work for a matching gift company?&#160;</strong><a href="http://give.uci.edu/ways/index.php#" onclick="window.open('https://secure.connect.uci.edu/show_module_fw2.aspx?sid=1735&amp;gid=3&amp;inframe=1&amp;cid=858&amp;nologo=1','HelpWindow','scrollbars,resizable,toolbar=yes,height=400,width=600');"><em>Find Out &gt;</em></a></p>
<p><strong>You can mail your matching gift to:</strong> <br/> UCI Gift Administration<br/> University Advancement<br/> 100 Theory, Suite 250<br/> Irvine, CA 92617</p>
<p><strong>For questions, please email or call:</strong><br/> <a href="mailto:matching-gifts@uci.edu">matching-gifts@uci.edu</a><br/> (949) 824-7631</p>
<div align="center"><hr align="center" size="1" width="100%"/></div>
<h3><a name="eft"></a>Electronic Fund Transfer (EFT)</h3>
<p>To make an Electronic Fund Transfer (EFT) donation, please contact:</p>
<p>Christie Israel<br/> Email:&#160;<a href="mailto:cisrael@uci.edu?subject=Electronic%20Fund%20Transfer">cisrael@uci.edu</a>&#160;<br/> Phone: 949-824-1509.</p>
<div align="center"><hr align="center" size="1" width="100%"/></div>
<h3><a name="stock"></a>Stock and Securities</h3>
<p>1. You can complete and print out the&#160;<a href="http://give.uci.edu/pdf/ways/State-Street-Securities-Donation-Form.pdf.">Stock and Securities Notification Form</a>&#160;and mail it to:</p>
<p><strong>UCI Gift Administration&#160;<br/> University Advancement<br/> 100 Theory, Suite 250<br/> Irvine, CA 92617</strong></p>
<p>2. Or, fax to:&#160;<strong>949-824-2774</strong></p>
<div align="center"><hr align="center" size="1" width="100%"/></div>
<h3>Planned Giving</h3>
<p>To learn about the many benefits of making a planned gift,<strong> </strong>visit<strong>: </strong><a href="http://www.plannedgiving.uci.edu/">http://www.plannedgiving.uci.edu/</a></p>
<div align="center"><hr align="center" size="1" width="100%"/></div>
<h3><a name="Endowed"></a>Endowed Funds</h3>
<p>Endowed funds are invested in perpetuity. A portion of the invested return is distributed annually to university priorities and designated programs, while the remaining portion of the return is reinvested back into the principal for market growth.&#160;This allows for endowment to provide both immediate funding and long-term financial security for the institution, ensuring that the fund will continue to benefit future generations of scholars, faculty, and patients.</p>
<p>To learn more, visit: <a href="http://give.uci.edu/give/endowed-funds.php">http://give.uci.edu/give/endowed-funds.php</a>.</p>
<div align="center"><hr align="center" size="1" width="100%"/></div>
<h3><a name="cfg"></a>Corporate and Foundation Giving</h3>
<p>Gifts from foundation and corporate partners advance knowledge, research and community initiatives that have a positive impact on our campus and the world.</p>
<ul>
<li>To make a gift on behalf of a corporation or foundation, please contact us by email <a href="mailto:UA-FR@uci.edu" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">UA-FR@exchange.uci.edu</a> or via telephone at (949) 824-0034.</li>
<li>If you are a UCI staff or faculty member interested in learning more about foundation relations, please visit <a href="http://grants.give.uci.edu/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">our website</a>.</li>
</ul>
</div>
  
